&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to work independently, take initiative, and manage responsibilities with minimal supervision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on leader and coach; thrives on the shop floor and in frontline engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High emotional intelligence with the ability to influence without authority.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable navigating ambiguity and building structure in evolving organizations.&lt;/li&gt;
