&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in AutoCAD for electrical design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of UL standards applicable to switchgear, NEC, CEC and power distribution equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail with a commitment to design accuracy, documentation quality, and adherence to established engineering processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite (Excel, Word, Outlook).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience in a custom switchgear, MCC, or power distribution manufacturing environment is desired.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
