&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Position Summary: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be part of the Estimating Department that will provide the Sales Division with support by performing proposal preparation and in-depth analysis of engineering and design.&lt;/p&gt;
