&lt;li&gt;Obtain and provide pricing for buyout items from approved vendor partners as requested by the Sales team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze RFQ documentation and summarize key requirements, risks, and project details for internal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the Sales team by communicating critical project information and ensuring quotation accuracy and completeness.&lt;/li&gt;
